Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:06.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:15.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:46.96,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}The One I've Set My Heart On
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:11.19,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Finral Roulacase, a member of the Black \NBulls Magic Knights Squad, was troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:14.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very important matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.80,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:21.55,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Finral's troubles had nothing \Nto do with a mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:23.70,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,...about tonight's mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:26.54,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A mixer, meaning a gathering \Nbetween men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It is a dinner intended to help \Nmen and women get acquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:34.62,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,When I set this up, three girls \Nagreed to come, and that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:37.02,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The more girls, the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:41.87,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But the problem is who \Nelse I'm going to bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:46.12,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's a delight, so I'm bringing him \Nfor sure. I just need one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.80,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:03.30,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.20,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.01,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Didja see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:25.82,top,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is what truly makes a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.82,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no. I know there are girls\Nwho like delinquents, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:33.21,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet ya!\NMy Crazy Cyclone's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:37.40,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is what truly makes a man!\NBrr-r-r-rm, brr-r-r-rm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.81,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Magna's too much of a delinquent. \NHe'd just scare them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.53,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Almost... I'm almost done
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.48,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,with my life-size statue of Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:00.36,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Marie. It feels like \Nyou're right next to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.51,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved little sister, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.99,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you truly are an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.99,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no. Even if I took him to a mixer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.25,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's more of an angel than any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.84,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a mixer \Nwith a hundred Maries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:17.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Marie was already an angel \Nbefore she was even born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.69,italics,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... A sister complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.71,italics,Girl C,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.95,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He'd definitely scare them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.69,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you were having a mixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.57,top,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:34.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have no idea what Gordon's \Nthinking, so that's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:34.29,top,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,No, really. You don't need to hold back. \NIt's not as if I don't like girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:57.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It might be fun to bring Charmy along,\Nsince she's sort of like a mascot character.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:01.52,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.88,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,This is so yummy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.26,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, could I get seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.80,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize. It's only been \Nfive minutes since we opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.97,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but we're out of ingredients, \Nso we must close for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.93,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.79,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The mixer'd be over in five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what I assume would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I could take Vanessa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I could go all-out and invite Yami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are girls \Nwho like older guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:46.63,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yami does hate gaudy types, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:52.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you three \Ndressed like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:55.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you showing too much skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:59.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What if you catch a cold? \NPut something warm over your stomachs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:01.00,italics,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.28,italics,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.31,italics,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,So overbearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.48,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, that leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.32,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,A mixer? Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Thanks for agreeing to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:20.50,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Luck looks decent, \Nso I'm sure things will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's a mixer, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Will this actually work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.94,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it looks like we're all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make sure they know \Nthat we're Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:39.89,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights are the most admired figures \Nin the Clover Kingdom, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:45.13,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Are mixers strong? I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm excited, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Hurry on through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:01.66,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go, too? I promise \NI won't get in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.88,sign_10213_108_City_in_the_Comm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(966,1)}City in the Common Realm: Nean
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.43,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sneak... Sneak, sneak... Sneak, sneak, sneak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.64,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard they were going to a mixer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.61,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried, I ended up following them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.08,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this. Why are\Nthey going to a mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.61,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This is the problem with lowly fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:36.60,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, it's not as if I like that\Nmuscle-brained shrimp or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.65,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who he hangs out \Nwith or what happens after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:43.75,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who am I even making excuses to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it was \Nsomewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.38,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.09,sign_11469_121_Pub_Mibawau_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Dreavy Hinker
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:11.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Looks like we all have our drinks,\Nso let's get right to the introductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ahead and start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:23.83,sign_11989_127_Finral_Roulacase,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Finral Roulacase\N{\fs20}21-Year-Old Member of the Black Bulls From Touta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.61,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 21 years old and from Touta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:23.03,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Finral Roulacase, the spatial \Nmagic user from the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:23.83,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.27,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,These are freshly picked moon blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.59,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Please take them as a \Ntoken of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.91,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! They're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:35.59,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,These only bloom at night \Non Mount Anahu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.44,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,They smell so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.34,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:43.06,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hook, line, and sinker! I'm finally \Ngoing to get a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:46.81,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But for that to happen, I need both \NAsta and Luck to do their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.61,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, introduce yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:51.35,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.77,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Am I just supposed to say what I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:54.61,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:09:02.64,sign_11989_127_Finral_Roulacase,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(526,997)}Luck Voltia\N{\fs20}18-Year-Old Member of the Black Bulls From Ibon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:59.25,top,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luck Voltia, and I'm 18 years old.\NI'm from Ibon and belong to the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:03.67,top,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,My hobbies include fighting tough \Nenemies in bloody, mortal combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.46,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't "fighting for your life"\Na wonderful phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:16.84,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce myself... A manly man should \Nprobably talk about his dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:17.87,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:26.29,sign_13533_146_Asta_15_Year_Old,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(487,999)}Asta\N{\fs20}15-Year-Old Member of the Black Bulls From Hage Village
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:25.60,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Asta. I'm fifteen. I'm from Hage\NVillage. I'm a member of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.02,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Um... my dream is to become \Nthe Wizard King someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.32,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.52,italics,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,That'll never happen. \NHe's just a kid, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.40,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,These two seem kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.40,top,,0000,0000,0000,,How d'ya like these biceps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.53,italics,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,...sketchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.53,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I heard they'd be Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:43.53,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,but they just had to be Black Bulls, \Nthe lowest of the low?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.93,italics,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,And if he's from Hage, isn't he a peasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.25,italics,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,Like, a total peasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.32,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never go out with any of these guys \Nif they didn't earn more than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.74,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,And if they're younger, shorter, \Nand socially beneath me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.50,italics,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:58.09,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... This seems to be going south.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:04.13,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We've introduced ourselves, \Nso now it's your turn, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep things rolling! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.73,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We're passing the baton to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.68,top,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Um... We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:18.26,sign_14688_165_Rebecca_Scarlet,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1001)}Rebecca Scarlet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:18.26,sign_14688_166_Helene_Barbary,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1001)}Helene Barbary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:18.26,sign_14688_167_Erika_Sitate_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1001)}Erika Sitate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.13,top,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Erika. I work at a dressmaker shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.77,top,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Helene, and I work as a hairdresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.56,top,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca. I work at a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.07,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,They're clearly losing interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so you all have \Nsolid jobs. That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I'd love to hear about your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.76,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love it if you made some clothes for me. \NWhat do you think would look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could cut my hair sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking of \Nchanging up my hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Could I eat at your place sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:41.93,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No reaction whatsoever! I need to think \Nof something they'd be interested in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.47,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,W-Want to hear about the Magic Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:47.45,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.00,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:49.92,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:55.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's great to hear. Well, I use spatial\Nmagic to go to all sorts of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Something I've done recently at my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.94,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:01.40,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:03.67,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Send me to the john.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.69,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.59,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Send me to the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:09.41,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.96,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Send me to my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.00,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:16.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I've done anything lately \Nother than move Yami around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:20.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Luck! You've been working hard! \NWhat have you done recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.43,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.51,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them something interesting \Nyou've done at work lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Helene and the other girls \Nreally want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.51,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Work, huh? Let's see... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.68,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, we ran into \Na group of ten bandits...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.89,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.08,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,...and I beat them all to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.88,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It was so brutal! And so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.82,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I could've easily killed them all,\Nbut I just broke three of their bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:44.36,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It completely backfired!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.24,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and when I fought this mage, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.78,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thanks, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.72,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go on and eat up, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.01,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:54.25,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear what Asta's been up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:57.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You protected the people of the\Nroyal capital, didn't you? Great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:02.97,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean the incident the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:04.65,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,When the capital was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:08.22,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Asta worked really \Nhard and got promoted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.51,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:14.14,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is going well. We just need to keep\Ntaking the conversation in this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.56,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,You must be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:20.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't manage to protect myself.\NThey put three holes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They hurt like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.00,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's all squishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:30.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Hey, don't poke at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.48,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,These two are useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.08,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I should've known a mixer \Nwouldn't work with these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:38.50,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All of our members suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow! Come on, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.21,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.25,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I heard them mention a mixer, \Nso I ended up tagging along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.11,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But thankfully, it doesn't \Nseem to be going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:02.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Like I {\i1}said{\i0}! I don't care \Nwhat happens to Shrimpsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.69,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:05.72,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, waitress!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.03,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Get me another beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get it yourself, insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.79,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:15.75,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,So you know about that huge incident \Nat the capital the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:20.07,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to be on bodyguard duty \Nfor a VIP in the capital that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:29.89,sign_19264_241___Lies__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(885,1)}< Lies >
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:23.96,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,and just happened to defeat \Na number of the intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.57,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:27.36,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,They gave me an exceptional promotion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.89,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,and bumped me up to \NIntermediate Magic Knight all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.76,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's a such a hassle, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.68,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm even that talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:37.12,sign_19264_241___Lies__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,536)}< This is true >
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.35,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:40.15,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. Maybe I'm a little intoxicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.08,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:48.65,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you were looking at a \Ndirty mag during all that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:52.11,main,Hurgh,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you talking \Nabout? Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.33,main,Hurgh,0000,0000,0000,,Shh, shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.72,main,Herf Herf,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You guys \Nnervous to be around us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.58,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! You don't have to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:04.65,italics,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,He just squeezed lemon all over\Nthe fried chicken without asking first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.88,italics,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,At least ask first...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.51,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this mixer from hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:13.11,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I've seen this \Nguy before. He's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:13.94,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:15.14,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:19.71,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,To think that my bronze magic \Nwould be so formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:22.40,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I even terrify myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:26.49,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You there, waitress! Get me another drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.78,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.78,main,Hurgh,0000,0000,0000,,Hurgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.78,top,Herf Herf,0000,0000,0000,,Herf herf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.74,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's the kind of magic \Nyou use when you cut hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.75,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I just go like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:43.75,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't take much magic, but you \Nneed really good control! Show me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.52,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.27,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes are so pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.31,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,He has such a cute smile,\Nbut there's danger behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.98,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might like that gap \Nmore than I want to admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:57.51,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... I think I'm starting \Nto like bad boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.64,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could you show me your magic, too, Luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:04.33,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! It's a bit cramped\Nin here, so let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.47,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.91,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:14.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And the sunrise looks really \Nbeautiful from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.19,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:19.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you there with my \Nspatial magic sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.61,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go camping with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.33,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:25.83,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want another drink? Excuse me,\Ncould we get another drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:30.59,italics,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bit gaudy and not really my type,\Nbut he's the best out of the three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.63,italics,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like a noble, and spatial magic\Nwould be really handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.09,italics,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, he's considerate and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.80,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Say, want to step out to the patio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.47,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:45.72,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure how things \Nwould go for a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.36,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,but I think things might just work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:52.99,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is so awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.04,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this lady keep \Nlooking away and down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.37,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is she mad? Did I do \Nsomething to make her mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.67,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. I need to liven things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:03.12,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure how, \Nbut I have to liven things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.00,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right! It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:05.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I love tatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:16.44,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to force yourself \Nto make small talk. This is dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.67,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Erika told me that I should \Nfind a good guy for the sake
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:23.34,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,of my siblings, so I came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:28.94,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't the real me, and I'm \Ntoo worried about my siblings at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:31.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you live with your siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.68,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I have three younger brothers \Nand two younger sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:41.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have five siblings, too,\Nthough we're not related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:44.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not with them right now,\Nbut they're all a bunch of little brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They annoyed me sometimes, \Nbut we had so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We used to all sleep in the same bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:56.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm in the Magic Knights, I get \Nmy own room, so it's a little easier,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:17:00.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but not having those fidgety little brats \Nsleeping next to me gets a bit lonely, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:04.63,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They can be a pain, but it \Ngets lonely when they're not around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:08.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! And you can act like a \Ndork in front of your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but you always want to impress your siblings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.30,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I totally get that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! They're actually having fun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.68,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.12,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.27,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,You just asked for a job out \Nof the blue, so I hired you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.79,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,but then you blew away some customers! \NWho do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:27.08,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:30.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you seem \Nlike a big sister, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:34.13,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely don't seem \Nlike the oldest, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have one brother who's the \Nsame age as me named Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.56,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:46.64,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having fun,\No great Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:49.49,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a little small to be one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:52.22,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:57.91,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,If a little twerp like you got in,\NI could probably get in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:01.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm surprised I made it in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:06.35,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,And being out with a flashy little \Nthing like this? I sure envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:10.39,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Bet you're desperate to catch yourself \Na Magic Knight, aren't ya, missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:16.87,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure I've seen you somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:21.26,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the girl who works \Nat the local restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:25.26,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,always carrying a kid on your back and\Nworking until you're drenched in sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:31.96,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Are all those brats yours? That must \Nmean your man walked out on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.65,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,No! That was my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:36.72,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, of course you'd like \Nto get yourself a Magic Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.86,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,and enjoy the easy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.57,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a man that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.07,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,come hang out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.91,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:52.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what your deal is, mister, \Nbut don't judge people by their appearances!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:55.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about her, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.07,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:03.39,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of amazing magic are you \Ngonna show me, widdle Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.67,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,What? A Magic Knight that can't use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.83,main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of lousy joke is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:13.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:30.67,main,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.27,main,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,That was a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.75,main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get more drinks somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:36.37,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:37.94,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.48,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.27,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boss! I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:43.88,main,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:59.29,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Asta. I feel so much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:02.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Sorry for ruining the mixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.16,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:11.57,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bit short, but he's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:20.42,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta... D-Do you have \Nanyone that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! There's somebody \NI've got my heart set on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.19,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.00,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:30.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She is! We're from the same—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.47,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you both the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:36.32,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come by my restaurant sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:37.84,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You can play with my siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,"Same"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:49.65,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The same squad?! Then... could... \Ncould that mean... mean m-m-m-me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:53.08,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, no, no! And what if it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:57.37,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I th-think... anything... anything of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:02.67,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, we spent so many \Nyears together in Hage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.64,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I'll become the \NWizard King and come for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:08.01,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please marry me then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:11.88,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I'm supporting him \Ndoesn't mean I'm going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:16.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's the \Npoint of a mixer, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:17.98,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:19.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:25.60,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he threw some drunkard to \Nthe ground. Black Bulls are so violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.07,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,She shot me down...
