Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.99,0:23:05.95,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:10.01,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}If Gordon, Grey, and Sekke\NWent to a Mixer Together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:10.01,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,If Gordon, Grey, and Sekke \NWent to a Mixer Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:10.01,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Bah-ha! Bah-ha-ha-haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.36,0:23:13.69,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Helene.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:15.01,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:16.28,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:19.10,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to be at a mixer \Nwith people as cute as you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:22.27,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be my friend? You will? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:22.27,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.27,0:23:26.52,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Could we exchange contact info? \NI'll write you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:26.52,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.69,0:23:30.53,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.43,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:37.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:41.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prove that even peasants \Ncan move up the ranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:45.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 29: "Path."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:51.14,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 29\N\N{\fs18}Path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:49.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not giving up is my magic!
